MediaDatabase

Class MediaMaker

  • java.lang.Object
    • MediaDatabase.MediaMaker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Actor, Director, Producer

    public abstract class MediaMaker
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This MediaMaker class is an abstract class that acts as the parent for all types of mediaMakers. Their corresponding media credits are accessed using MediaMaker subclasses as the key in a hashmap. The abstract class will contain all of the class features for each of its subclasses (Actor, Director, Producer). This class can be expanded (additional variables) for additional information about each media maker.
